	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require a miniature platinum sword with a grip and pommel of copper and zinc worth at least 250 gp.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Summoning</strong></p><ul><li><p>You create a sword-shaped plane of force that hovers within range for the duration.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>When the sword appears, make a melee spell attack against one target within 5 feet of it.</p></li><li><p>It is immune to &amp;reference[poison apply=false]{poison} and &amp;reference[psychic ]{psychic} damage, and immune to all conditions except cover, &amp;reference[hasted apply=false]{hasted}, &amp;reference[invisible apply=false]{invisible}, &amp;reference[obscured]{obscured}, and &amp;reference[slowed apply=false]{slowed}.</p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> As a Bonus Action on each of your turns, you can move the sword up to 20 feet to a spot you can see. The sword can then make another attack against a target within 5 feet of it.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Melee Spell Attack</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 3d10 force]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Miss:</strong> No damage.</p></li></ul>",
